The demon prepares to charge again but before it does Victor appears behind it,wielding his gigantic sword and
hacks it down pre-emptively,smearing the demons onyx blood on his magical armour.'That was satisfying,I should
have watched it strike you dead,given how pathetic you are in combat.'He remarks,in absolute glee.This barbaric
fool how dare he jeer at me after releasing that grotesque thing.Should I react to this maniac.
